chewmail
------------------------------------------

mail archiver for various mailbox formats

A Perl-based mail archiver. It uses Mail::Box so supports any mailbox
format it does. It can filter messages into mbox's based on the
message's date and other criteria.

Additional CPAN modules need to be installed:

    $ perl -MCPAN -e 'install $_ for @ARGV' \
      Mail::Box::Manager \
      Mail::Message \
      Date::Format \
      Date::Parse

Runtime requirements:
  perl

Build requirements:
  quilt

